{"tid":837882,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"[冠軍級band show] 9月28恆管band soc第六屆迎新band show序。樂","createTime":"2018-09-26T16:47:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T03:38:23.000Z","uid":186882,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5461099812c0b4da6c12aff8d0900cffcf0dba1c","tid":837882,"uid":186882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T16:47:46.000Z","msg":"[冠軍級band show] 9月28恆管band soc第六屆迎新band show序。樂<br />\n<br />\n時間： 9月28日 星期五 8-10pm<br />\n地點： 九龍新蒲崗五芳街8號利嘉工業大廈4B室<br />\n票價: $70/人<br />\n<br />\n買飛呢度<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSe_uWJ9P2S7PkCD7MEH65sijmvWlqWeE6uNd0-V5ilIN0HKaw/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSe_uWJ9P2S7PkCD7MEH65sijmvWlqWeE6uNd0-V5ilIN0HKaw%2Fviewform&d=PUc9GgcopHu7ojsgqDnXgE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=ccca3354\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSe_uWJ9P2S7PkCD7MEH65sijmvWlqWeE6uNd0-V5ilIN0HKaw/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n點解我會話係冠軍級band show,  因為個line up 4 隊都係香港indie band界勁旅， 全部都攞過冠軍既<br />\n<br />\nAndy is typing...<br />\nPersons music bamd legend 2016 年冠軍<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/AQR373NkhZE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAQR373NkhZE&d=PUc9GgcopHu7ojsgqDnXgE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=77d69f56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/AQR373NkhZE</a><br />\n<br />\nStereo is the answer<br />\nYamaha asian beat 2015 香港區冠軍<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0xKsrviym-g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0xKsrviym-g&d=PUc9GgcopHu7ojsgqDnXgE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=d91807fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0xKsrviym-g</a><br />\n<br />\nCow head<br />\nPersons music bamd legend 2016 季軍 &gt; 2017 亞軍 &gt; 2018 冠軍<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3aNOiYYFzuk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3aNOiYYFzuk&d=PUc9GgcopHu7ojsgqDnXgE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=d70d38ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3aNOiYYFzuk</a><br />\n<br />\nVIRT<br />\n青協2017 樂隊大賽冠軍<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cW9TloM6lgo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcW9TloM6lgo&d=PUc9GgcopHu7ojsgqDnXgE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=f299d309\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cW9TloM6lgo</a><br />\n<br />\n除左上列冠軍外， 佢地其實呢幾年參加既青協， persons等等好多不同比賽都係3甲之列<br />\n隊隊技術編曲都係一流。 只係香港娛樂圈唔會留意佢地<br />\n今次恆管band soc可以請到佢地， 仲要門票只係70 蚊<br />\n真係<br />\n呢d band show無得賺，搞手只求打個和，大家開開心心玩返晚。<br />\n<br />\n希望你地有興趣可以按入去條link報名<br />\n攪手過份佛系， 唔係我like左呢d band根本唔知有場line up咁正既show"},{"pid":"0d40789368be91efbc02add92acaeb45dedeb39e","tid":837882,"uid":186882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T16:48:34.000Z","msg":"屌， 出左兩個post添"},{"pid":"63f8010acd5578b0ec2ce201e0e382b45ce2bcf3","tid":837882,"uid":186882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T17:15:39.000Z","msg":"介紹下4 隊band先<br />\n首先andy is typing...<br />\n不得不提係鼓手kelvin<br />\n佢手鼓勁撚到癲<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/JGwSLC2ipfw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FJGwSLC2ipfw&d=PUc9GgcopHu7ojsgqDnXgE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=12602109\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/JGwSLC2ipfw</a><br />\n唔單止快狠準， 仲周不時chok樣抛鼓棍<br />\n睇佢打鼓爽過睇雜技<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/D8fbubikkKM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FD8fbubikkKM&d=PUc9GgcopHu7ojsgqDnXgE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=53d45d3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/D8fbubikkKM</a><br />\n<br />\n另外首3:1 都好正<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0xevMJKgz7o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0xevMJKgz7o&d=PUc9GgcopHu7ojsgqDnXgE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=a2d068e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0xevMJKgz7o</a>"},{"pid":"958ca1c779d42b1ff5d87